#: ../../content/applications/essentials.rst:3
msgid "Odoo essentials"
msgstr "Odoo grundlæggende"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:3
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Aktiviteter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:7
msgid "*Activities* are follow-up tasks tied to a record in an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*Aktiviteter* er opfølgningsopgaver knyttet til en post i en Odoo-database."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:11
msgid ""
"The icon used to display activities varies, depending on the :ref:`activity "
"type <activities/types>`:"
msgstr ""
"Ikonet, der bruges til at vise aktiviteter, varierer afhængigt "
"af :ref:`aktivitetstypen <activities/types>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:14
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(clock)` icon: the default activities icon."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(ur)`-ikon: standardikonet for aktiviteter."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:15
msgid ":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` icon: a phone call is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telefon)`-ikon: et telefonopkald er planlagt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:16
msgid ":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(envelope)` icon: an email is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-envelope` :guilabel:`(konvolut)`-ikon: en e-mail er planlagt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:17
msgid ":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`(check)` icon: a \"to-do\" is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`(flueben)`-ikon: et \"gøremål\" er planlagt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:18
msgid ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`(people)` icon: a meeting is scheduled."
msgstr ":icon:`fa-users` :guilabel:`(personer)`-ikon: et møde er planlagt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:19
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)` icon: a document is scheduled to be "
"uploaded."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)`-ikon: et dokument er planlagt til at "
"blive uploadet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:20
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`(request signature)` icon: a signature "
"request is scheduled."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`(anmod om underskrift)`-ikon: en "
"underskriftsanmodning er planlagt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:23
msgid "Schedule activities"
msgstr "Planlæg aktiviteter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:25
msgid ""
"Activities can be scheduled on any page of the database that contains "
"a :ref:`chatter <activities/chatter>` thread, :ref:`Kanban view <activities/"
"kanban>`, :ref:`list view <activities/list>`, or :ref:`activities view "
"<activities/activity>` of an application."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviteter kan planlægges på enhver side i databasen, der indeholder "
"en :ref:`chatter <activities/chatter>`-tråd, :ref:`Kanban-visning "
"<activities/kanban>`, :ref:`listevisning <activities/list>` "
"eller :ref:`aktivitetsvisning <activities/activity>` af en applikation."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:32
msgid "Chatter"
msgstr "Chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:34
msgid "Activities can be created from the chatter on any record."
msgstr "Aktiviteter kan oprettes fra chatteren på enhver post."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:36
msgid ""
"To schedule a new activity, click the :guilabel:`Activities` button, located "
"at the top of the chatter. In the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up "
"window that appears, :ref:`fill out the Schedule Activity form <activities/"
"form>`."
msgstr ""
"For at planlægge en ny aktivitet skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Aktiviteter`, som findes øverst i chatten. I pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet`, der vises, skal du :ref:`udfylde "
"formularen Planlæg aktivitet <activities/form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "New activity type form."
msgstr "Ny aktivitetstypeformular."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:47
msgid "Kanban view"
msgstr "Kanban-visning"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:49
msgid ""
"Activities can also be created from the :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviteter kan også oprettes fra :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)`-visningen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:51
msgid ""
"To do so, click on the |clock| located at the bottom of an individual record."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du klikke på |clock|, der findes nederst på en "
"individuel post."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:53
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`+ Schedule An Activity`, then proceed to :ref:`fill out the "
"Schedule Activity form <activities/form>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`+ Planlæg en aktivitet`, og fortsæt derefter med "
"at :ref:`udfylde formularen Planlæg aktivitet <activities/form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "Kanban view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr ""
"Kanban-visning af CRM-pipelinen og muligheden for at planlægge en aktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:79
msgid ""
"If a record already has a scheduled activity, the |clock| is replaced by the "
"icon that represents the existing scheduled activity. Click on the activity "
"type's icon to schedule another activity."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en post allerede har en planlagt aktivitet, erstattes |clock| af "
"ikonet, der repræsenterer den eksisterende planlagte aktivitet. Klik på "
"aktivitetstypens ikon for at planlægge en anden aktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:67
msgid "List view"
msgstr "Listevisning"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:69
msgid ""
"Activities can also be created from a :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(list)` view."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviteter kan også oprettes fra en :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(liste)`-visning."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:71
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Activities` column is hidden, reveal it using "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings adjust)` icon in the far-"
"right of the top row."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kolonnen :guilabel:`Aktiviteter` er skjult, kan du få den vist ved "
"hjælp af :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(indstillingsjustering)`-"
"ikonet helt til højre i den øverste række."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:74
msgid ""
"Then, click on the |clock| for the record the activity is being added to, "
"and click :guilabel:`+ Schedule an activity`. Proceed to :ref:`fill out the "
"Schedule Activity form <activities/form>` that appears."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på |clock| for den post, aktiviteten tilføjes til, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`+ Planlæg en aktivitet`. Fortsæt med at :ref:`udfylde "
"formularen Planlæg aktivitet <activities/form>`, der vises."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "List view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr ""
"Listevisning af CRM-pipelinen og muligheden for at planlægge en aktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:89
msgid "Activity view"
msgstr "Aktivitetsvisning"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:91
msgid ""
"Most applications in Odoo have an *Activity* view available. If available, a "
"|clock| is visible in the top-right corner of the main menu bar, amongst the "
"other view option icons."
msgstr ""
"Většina aplikací v Odoo má k dispozici pohled *Aktivity*. Je-li k dispozici, "
"zobrazí se |clock| v pravém horním rohu hlavní nabídky mezi ostatními "
"ikonami možností pohledu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:94
msgid "To open the activity view, click the |clock|."
msgstr "Pro otevření pohledu aktivit klikněte na |clock|."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "Top-right menu with the Activities icon called out."
msgstr "Nabídka v pravém horním rohu se zvýrazněnou ikonou Aktivity."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:100
msgid ""
"In this view, all the available activities are listed in the columns, while "
"the horizontal entries represent all the individual records."
msgstr ""
"V tomto pohledu jsou všechny dostupné aktivity uvedeny ve sloupcích, zatímco "
"vodorovné záznamy představují všechny jednotlivé záznamy."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:103
msgid ""
"Activities that appear green have a due date in the future, activities that "
"appear orange are due today, while activities appearing red are overdue."
msgstr ""
"Aktivity, které se zobrazují zeleně, mají termín dokončení v budoucnosti, "
"aktivity zobrazené oranžově jsou splatné dnes, zatímco aktivity zobrazené "
"červeně jsou po splatnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:106
msgid ""
"Color bars in each column represent records for specific activity types, and "
"display a number indicating how many activities are scheduled for that type."
msgstr ""
"Farvede bjælker i hver kolonne repræsenterer poster for specifikke "
"aktivitetstyper og viser et tal, der angiver, hvor mange aktiviteter der er "
"planlagt for den pågældende type."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:109
msgid ""
"If multiple activity types are scheduled for a record, a number appears in "
"the box, indicating the total number of scheduled activities."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je pro záznam naplánováno více typů aktivit, zobrazí se v poli číslo "
"udávající celkový počet naplánovaných aktivit."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:113
msgid ""
"Activity colors, and their relation to an activity's due date, are "
"consistent throughout Odoo, regardless of the activity type, or the view."
msgstr ""
"Barvy aktivit a jejich vztah k datu splatnosti aktivity jsou v celém Odoo "
"konzistentní bez ohledu na typ aktivity nebo pohled."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:116
msgid ""
"To schedule an activity for a record, hover over the corresponding field. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon that appears, and "
"then :ref:`fill out the Schedule Activity form <activities/form>`."
msgstr ""
"For at planlægge en aktivitet for en post skal du holde markøren over det "
"tilsvarende felt. Klik på :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)`-ikonet, der "
"vises, og :ref:`udfyld derefter formularen Planlæg aktivitet <activities/"
"form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid ""
"Activity view of the CRM pipeline and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Pohled aktivit na CRM proces a možnost naplánovat aktivitu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:127
msgid "Schedule Activity form"
msgstr "Formulář Naplánovat aktivitu"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:129
msgid ""
"Activities can be scheduled from many different places, such as from "
"the :ref:`chatter <activities/chatter>` of a record, or from one of multiple "
"views in an application, when available: the :ref:`Kanban view <activities/"
"kanban>`, :ref:`list view <activities/list>`, or :ref:`activity view "
"<activities/activity>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivity lze naplánovat z mnoha různých míst, například z :ref:`chatter "
"<activities/chatter>` záznamu nebo z některého z více pohledů v aplikaci, je-"
"li k dispozici: :ref:`pohledu Kanban <activities/kanban>`, :ref:`pohledu "
"seznamu <activities/list>` nebo :ref:`pohledu aktivit <activities/activity>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:134
msgid "Enter the following information on the form:"
msgstr "Indtast følgende oplysninger på formularen:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Activity Type`: select the type of activity from the drop-down "
"menu. The default options "
"are: :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Call`, :guilabel:`Meeting`, "
"or :guilabel:`To-Do`. Depending on what other applications are installed, "
"additional options may be available."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aktivitetstype`: vælg aktivitetstypen fra rullemenuen. "
"Standardindstillingerne er: :guilabel:`E-"
"mail`, :guilabel:`Opkald`, :guilabel:`Møde` eller :guilabel:`Gøremål`. "
"Afhængigt af hvilke andre applikationer der er installeret, kan der være "
"yderligere muligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Summary`: enter a short title for the activity, such as `Discuss "
"Proposal`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Resumé`: indtast en kort titel til aktiviteten, f.eks. `Drøft "
"forslag`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date`: using the calendar popover, select the activity's "
"deadline."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum splatnosti`: pomocí kalendáře vyberte konečný termín "
"aktivity."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:141
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Assigned to`: by default, the current user populates this field. "
"To assign a different user to the activity, select them from the drop-down "
"menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Přiřazeno`: ve výchozím nastavení je toto pole vyplněno aktuálním "
"uživatelem. Chcete-li aktivitu přiřadit jinému uživateli, vyberte ho z "
"rozevírací nabídky."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Notes`: add any additional information for the activity in this "
"field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bemærkninger`: tilføj eventuelle yderligere oplysninger om "
"aktiviteten i dette felt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:145
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window is completed, click one "
"of the following buttons:"
msgstr ""
"Når pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet` er udfyldt, skal du klikke "
"på en af følgende knapper:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Open Calendar`: opens the user's calendar to add and schedule the "
"activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Åbn kalender`: åbner brugerens kalender for at tilføje og "
"planlægge aktiviteten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:150
msgid ""
"Click on the desired date and time for the activity, and a :guilabel:`New "
"Event` pop-up window appears. The summary from the *Schedule Activity* pop-"
"up window populates the :guilabel:`Title` field."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na požadované datum a čas aktivity a zobrazí se vyskakovací "
"okno :guilabel:`Nová událost`. Shrnutí z vyskakovacího okna *Naplánovat "
"aktivitu* se vyplní do pole :guilabel:`Název`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:154
msgid ""
"Enter the information in the :guilabel:`New Event` pop-up window, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to schedule it. Once scheduled, the activity "
"is added to the chatter under the :guilabel:`Planned Activities` section."
msgstr ""
"Zadejte informace do vyskakovacího okna :guilabel:`Nová událost` a poté "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Uložit a zavřít`, aby byla naplánována. Po "
"naplánování je aktivita přidána do chatter v sekci :guilabel:`Plánované "
"aktivity`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:159
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Open Calendar` button **only** appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Activity Type` is set to either :guilabel:`Call` "
"or :guilabel:`Meeting`."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Åbn kalender` vises **kun**, "
"hvis :guilabel:`Aktivitetstype` er indstillet til enten :guilabel:`Opkald` "
"eller :guilabel:`Møde`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:162
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: schedules the activity, and adds the activity to the "
"chatter under :guilabel:`Planned Activities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlæg`: planlægger aktiviteten og tilføjer aktiviteten til "
"chatten under :guilabel:`Planlagte aktiviteter`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule & Mark as Done`: adds the details of the activity to the "
"chatter under :guilabel:`Today`. The activity is not scheduled, and is "
"automatically marked as done."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlæg og marker som udført`: tilføjer detaljerne for "
"aktiviteten til chatten under :guilabel:`I dag`. Aktiviteten er ikke "
"planlagt og markeres automatisk som udført."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:166
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Done & Schedule Next`: adds the details of the activity to the "
"chatter under :guilabel:`Today`. The activity is not scheduled, is "
"automatically marked as done, and a new :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up "
"window appears."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udført og planlæg næste`: tilføjer detaljerne for aktiviteten til "
"chatten under :guilabel:`I dag`. Aktiviteten er ikke planlagt, markeres "
"automatisk som udført, og et nyt pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet` "
"vises."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:169
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancel`: discards any changes made on the :guilabel:`Schedule "
"Activity` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Annuller`: forkaster eventuelle ændringer, der er foretaget i pop "
"op-vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "View of CRM leads and the option to schedule an activity."
msgstr "Zobrazení CRM příležitostí a možnost naplánovat aktivitu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:178
msgid "All scheduled activities"
msgstr "Všechny naplánované aktivity"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:180
msgid ""
"To view a consolidated list of activities, organized by application, click "
"the |clock| in the header menu, located in the top-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li zobrazit konsolidovaný seznam aktivit uspořádaný podle aplikace, "
"klikněte v hlavní nabídce v pravém horním rohu na |clock|."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:183
msgid ""
"If any activities are scheduled, the number of activities appear in a red "
"bubble on the |clock|."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er planlagt aktiviteter, vises antallet af aktiviteter i en rød "
"boble på |clock|."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:186
msgid ""
"All activities for each application are further divided into subsections, "
"indicating where in the application the activity is to be completed. Each "
"sub-section lists the number of scheduled activities that "
"are :guilabel:`Late`, due :guilabel:`Today`, and scheduled in "
"the :guilabel:`Future`."
msgstr ""
"Všechny aktivity pro každou aplikaci jsou dále rozděleny do podsekcí, které "
"udávají, kde v aplikaci má být aktivita dokončena. Každá podsekce uvádí "
"počet naplánovaných aktivit, které jsou :guilabel:`Opožděné`, "
"splatné :guilabel:`Dnes` a naplánované v :guilabel:`Budoucnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:192
msgid ""
"In the *Time Off* application, one activity is scheduled to be done in the "
"*All Time Off* requests dashboard, and six activities are scheduled to be "
"done in the *Allocations* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"I applikationen *Fravær* er der planlagt én aktivitet, der skal udføres i "
"dashboardet *Alle fraværsanmodninger*, og seks aktiviteter, der skal udføres "
"i dashboardet *Tildelinger*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:195
msgid ""
"These requests appear in two separate lists in the all activities drop-down "
"menu: one labeled `Time Off` and one labeled `Time Off Allocation`."
msgstr ""
"Tyto žádosti se zobrazují ve dvou samostatných seznamech v rozevírací "
"nabídce všech aktivit: jeden označený `Fri` a jeden označený `Přidělení "
"volna`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:0
msgid ""
"The list of activities that is accessed from the main menu bar. Two entries "
"for the Time\n"
"Off application are highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Listen over aktiviteter, der tilgås fra hovedmenulinjen. To poster for "
"applikationen Fravær er fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:204
msgid ""
"The option to :ref:`Request a Document <documents/request>` is available at "
"the bottom of the list of all scheduled activities."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :ref:`Vyžádat dokument <documents/request>` je k dispozici ve spodní "
"části seznamu všech naplánovaných aktivit."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:210
msgid "Activity types"
msgstr "Aktivitetstyper"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:212
msgid ""
"To view the currently configured types of activities in the database, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Discuss section --> Activities "
"setting --> Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"For at se de aktuelt konfigurerede typer af aktiviteter i databasen, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Beskeder --> Aktiviteter --> "
"Aktivitetstyper`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid ""
"Activity Types button in the Settings application under the Discuss section."
msgstr ""
"Knappen Aktivitetstyper i applikationen Indstillinger under afsnittet "
"Beskeder."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:219
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals the :guilabel:`Activity Types` page, where the existing "
"activity types are found."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner siden :guilabel:`Aktivitetstyper`, hvor de eksisterende "
"aktivitetstyper findes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:222
msgid ""
"Individual applications have a list of *Activity Types* dedicated to that "
"application. For example, to view and edit the activities available for the "
"*CRM* application, go to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"De enkelte applikationer har en liste over *Aktivitetstyper*, der er "
"dedikeret til den pågældende applikation. For eksempel for at se og redigere "
"de aktiviteter, der er tilgængelige for applikationen *CRM*, skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`CRM-app --> Konfiguration --> Aktivitetstyper`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "The list of activity types already configured and available."
msgstr ""
"Listen over aktivitetstyper, der allerede er konfigureret og tilgængelige."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:231
msgid "Edit activity types"
msgstr "Redigere aktivitetstyper"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:233
msgid ""
"To edit an existing :ref:`activity type <activities/types>`, click on the "
"activity type, and the activity type form loads."
msgstr ""
"For at redigere en eksisterende :ref:`aktivitetstype <activities/types>`, "
"klik på aktivitetstypen, så indlæses formularen for aktivitetstypen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:236
msgid ""
"Make any desired changes to the activity type form. The form automatically "
"saves, but it can be saved manually at any time by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save Manually` option, represented by a :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` icon, located in the top-left corner of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Foretag eventuelle ønskede ændringer i formularen for aktivitetstypen. "
"Formularen gemmes automatisk, men den kan gemmes manuelt når som helst ved "
"at klikke på indstillingen :guilabel:`Gem manuelt`, repræsenteret af "
"et :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` ikon, placeret i "
"øverste venstre hjørne af siden."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:241
msgid "Create new activity types"
msgstr "Oprette nye aktivitetstyper"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:243
msgid ""
"To create a new :ref:`activity type <activities/types>`, "
"click :guilabel:`New` from the :guilabel:`Activity Types` page, and a blank "
"activity type form loads."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li vytvořit nový :ref:`typ aktivity <activities/types>`, klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Nový` na stránce :guilabel:`Typy aktivit` a načte se prázdný "
"formulář typu aktivity."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:246
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for the activity type at the top of the form, then "
"enter the following information on the form."
msgstr ""
"Do pole :guilabel:`Název` v horní části formuláře zadejte název typu "
"aktivity a poté do formuláře zadejte následující informace."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:250
msgid "Activity Settings section"
msgstr "Afsnit med aktivitetsindstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:252
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: Using the drop-down menu, select an action associated "
"with this new activity type. Some actions trigger specific behaviors after "
"an activity is scheduled, such as:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Handling`: Brug rullemenuen til at vælge en handling, der er "
"knyttet til denne nye aktivitetstype. Nogle handlinger udløser specifikke "
"adfærdsmønstre, efter at en aktivitet er planlagt, såsom:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload Document`: If selected, a link to upload a document is "
"automatically added to the planned activity in the chatter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Upload dokument`: Hvis valgt, tilføjes automatisk et link til "
"upload af et dokument til den planlagte aktivitet i chatten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Call` or :guilabel:`Meeting`: If selected, users have the option "
"to open their calendar to select a date and time for the activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hovor` nebo :guilabel:`Schůzka`: Pokud je vybráno, uživatelé mají "
"možnost otevřít svůj kalendář a vybrat datum a čas aktivity."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:259
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Request Signature`: If selected, a link to open a signature "
"request pop-up window is automatically added to the planned activity in the "
"chatter. This requires the Odoo *Sign* application to be installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Požádat o podpis`: Pokud je vybráno, odkaz na otevření "
"vyskakovacího okna s požadavkem na podpis se automaticky přidá k plánované "
"aktivitě v chatteru. To vyžaduje nainstalovanou aplikaci Odoo *e-Signatur*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:264
msgid ""
"Available activity types vary based on the installed applications in the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Tilgængelige aktivitetstyper varierer afhængigt af de installerede "
"applikationer i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:266
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Folder`: Select a specific :ref:`folder <documents/folders>` to "
"save a document to. This field **only** appears if :guilabel:`Upload "
"Document` is selected for the :guilabel:`Action`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mappe`: Vælg en specifik :ref:`mappe <documents/folders>` at "
"gemme et dokument i. Dette felt vises **kun**, hvis :guilabel:`Upload "
"dokument` er valgt for :guilabel:`Handling`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:269
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default User`: Select a user from the drop-down menu to "
"automatically assign this activity to the selected user when this activity "
"type is scheduled. If this field is left blank, the activity is assigned to "
"the user who creates the activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardbruger`: Vælg en bruger fra rullemenuen for automatisk at "
"tildele denne aktivitet til den valgte bruger, når denne aktivitetstype "
"planlægges. Hvis dette felt efterlades tomt, tildeles aktiviteten til den "
"bruger, der opretter aktiviteten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:272
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Summary`: enter a note to include whenever this activity "
"type is created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardresumé`: indtast en note, der skal inkluderes, når denne "
"aktivitetstype oprettes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:275
msgid ""
"The information in the :guilabel:`Default User` and :guilabel:`Default "
"Summary` fields are included when an activity is created. However, they can "
"be altered before the activity is scheduled or saved."
msgstr ""
"Oplysningerne i felterne :guilabel:`Standardbruger` "
"og :guilabel:`Standardresumé` medtages, når en aktivitet oprettes. De kan "
"dog ændres, før aktiviteten planlægges eller gemmes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:279
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keep Done`: Tick this checkbox to keep activities that have been "
"marked as `Done` visible in the :ref:`activity view <activities/activity>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Behold udført`: Marker dette afkrydsningsfelt for at holde "
"aktiviteter, der er markeret som `Udført`, synlige "
"i :ref:`aktivitetsvisningen <activities/activity>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:281
msgid ":guilabel:`Default Note`: enter any notes to appear with the activity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardnote`: indtast eventuelle noter, der skal vises med "
"aktiviteten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:284
msgid "Next Activity section"
msgstr "Afsnit Næste aktivitet"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:286
msgid ""
"It is possible to have another activity either suggested or triggered. To do "
"so, configure the :guilabel:`Next Activity` section."
msgstr ""
"Det er muligt at få foreslået eller udløst en anden aktivitet. For at gøre "
"dette, skal du konfigurere afsnittet :guilabel:`Næste aktivitet`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:289
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Chaining Type`: select either :guilabel:`Suggest Next Activity` "
"or :guilabel:`Trigger Next Activity` from the drop-down menu. Depending on "
"the selected option, either the :guilabel:`Suggest` or :guilabel:`Trigger` "
"field is displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kædetype`: vælg enten :guilabel:`Foreslå næste aktivitet` "
"eller :guilabel:`Udløs næste aktivitet` fra rullemenuen. Afhængigt af den "
"valgte mulighed vises enten feltet :guilabel:`Foreslå` "
"eller :guilabel:`Udløs`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:294
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Chaining Type` field does **not** appear if :guilabel:`Upload "
"Document` is selected for the :guilabel:`Action`."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Kædetype` vises **ikke**, hvis :guilabel:`Upload dokument` "
"er valgt for :guilabel:`Handling`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:297
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggest/Trigger`: depending on what is selected for "
"the :guilabel:`Chaining Type`, this field either "
"displays :guilabel:`Suggest` or :guilabel:`Trigger`. Using the drop-down "
"menu, select the activity to recommend or schedule as a follow-up task to "
"the activity type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Foreslå/Udløs`: afhængigt af hvad der er valgt "
"for :guilabel:`Kædetype`, viser dette felt enten :guilabel:`Foreslå` "
"eller :guilabel:`Udløs`. Brug rullemenuen til at vælge den aktivitet, der "
"skal anbefales eller planlægges som en opfølgningsopgave til aktivitetstypen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:300
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: configure when the next activity is suggested or "
"triggered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlæg`: konfigurer, hvornår den næste aktivitet foreslås eller "
"udløses."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:302
msgid ""
"First, enter a numerical value indicating when the activity is suggested or "
"triggered."
msgstr ""
"Indtast først en numerisk værdi, der angiver, hvornår aktiviteten foreslås "
"eller udløses."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:304
msgid ""
"Next to this field, a :guilabel:`Days` field is visible. "
"Click :guilabel:`Days`, the default option, to reveal a drop-down menu. "
"Select the desired time-frame option from the list. The options "
"are :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, or :guilabel:`Months`."
msgstr ""
"Ved siden af dette felt er et :guilabel:`Dage`-felt synligt. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Dage`, standardindstillingen, for at vise en rullemenu. Vælg "
"den ønskede tidsramme fra listen. Mulighederne "
"er :guilabel:`Dage`, :guilabel:`Uger` eller :guilabel:`Måneder`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:308
msgid ""
"Lastly, using the drop-down menu, select whether the activity is scheduled "
"or triggered either :guilabel:`after previous activity deadline` "
"or :guilabel:`after completion date`."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst skal du bruge rullemenuen til at vælge, om aktiviteten planlægges "
"eller udløses enten :guilabel:`efter tidligere aktivitetsfrist` "
"eller :guilabel:`efter færdiggørelsesdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:None
msgid "A new Activity form with all the fields filled out."
msgstr "En ny aktivitetsformular med alle felter udfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:316
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:317
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss/team_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss/team_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/activities.rst:318
msgid ":doc:`../sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:5
msgid "Contacts"
msgstr "Adressebog"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:7
msgid ""
"Contacts are created in the **Contacts** application for customers the "
"company does business with through Odoo. A contact is a repository of vital "
"business information, facilitating communication and business transactions."
msgstr ""
"Kontakty jsou vytvářeny v aplikaci **Kontakter** pro zákazníky, se kterými "
"společnost obchoduje prostřednictvím Odoo. Kontakt je úložiště důležitých "
"obchodních informací, které usnadňuje komunikaci a obchodní transakce."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:12
msgid "Contact form"
msgstr "Kontaktformular"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create a new contact, navigate to the :menuselection:`Contacts app`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. A new form appears where various contact information "
"can be added."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny kontakt skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Adressebog-"
"appen` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. En ny formular vises, hvor forskellige "
"kontaktoplysninger kan tilføjes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:18
msgid ""
"Some fields may be slightly different depending on the :ref:`fiscal "
"localization <fiscal_localizations/packages>` that is installed on the "
"databse."
msgstr ""
"Nogle felter kan være lidt forskellige afhængigt af den :ref:`skattemæssige "
"lokalisering <fiscal_localizations/packages>`, der er installeret på "
"databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:22
msgid "Contact type"
msgstr "Kontakttype"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:24
msgid ""
"Odoo allows for both *Individual* and *Company* contacts. Select "
"either :guilabel:`Individual` or :guilabel:`Company`, depending on the type "
"of contact that is being added."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tillader både *individuelle* og *virksomheds*kontakter. Vælg "
"enten :guilabel:`Individuel` eller :guilabel:`Virksomhed`, afhængigt af "
"typen af kontakt, der tilføjes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:28
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Navn"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:30
msgid ""
"First, fill in the name of the contact. This is how the name appears "
"throughout the database. This field is **mandatory**."
msgstr ""
"Udfyld først kontaktens navn. Sådan vises navnet i hele databasen. Dette "
"felt er **obligatorisk**."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Individual` contacts can have a :guilabel:`Company` contact "
"linked to it. After selecting :guilabel:`Individual`, a "
"new :guilabel:`Company Name...` field appears below the first name field."
msgstr ""
"Kontakty typu :guilabel:`Jednotlivec` mohou mít připojený kontakt "
"typu :guilabel:`Společnost`. Po výběru možnosti :guilabel:`Jednotlivec` se "
"pod polem pro křestní jméno zobrazí nové pole :guilabel:`Název "
"společnosti...`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:39
msgid "Address"
msgstr "Adresse"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:41
msgid ""
"Next, enter the :guilabel:`Address` of the contact. If "
"the :guilabel:`Individual` option is chosen, then the *type of address* can "
"be chosen from a drop-down menu. Options for this drop-down menu "
"include: :guilabel:`Contact`, :guilabel:`Invoice "
"Address`, :guilabel:`Delivery Address`, :guilabel:`Follow-up Address`, "
"and :guilabel:`Other Address`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast derefter kontaktens :guilabel:`Adresse`. Hvis "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Individuel` vælges, kan *adressetypen* vælges fra "
"en rullemenu. Indstillinger for denne rullemenu "
"inkluderer: :guilabel:`Kontakt`, :guilabel:`Faktureringsadresse`, :guilabel:`Leveringsadresse`, :guilabel:`Opfølgningsadresse` "
"og :guilabel:`Anden adresse`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:None
msgid "The contact type drop-down on a new contact creation form."
msgstr ""
"Rullelisten for kontakttype i en formular til oprettelse af ny kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:50
msgid "Additional fields"
msgstr "Yderligere felter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Additional details are included on the initial form. The following fields "
"are available:"
msgstr ""
"Yderligere oplysninger er inkluderet på den oprindelige formular. Følgende "
"felter er tilgængelige:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Job Position`: list the contact's job position (only available "
"on :guilabel:`Individual`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jobtitel`: angiv kontaktens jobtitel (kun tilgængelig "
"ved :guilabel:`Person`)."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax ID`: the identification number used for tax and accounting "
"purposes. This may appear as :guilabel:`Identification Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Citizen ID` depending on the country."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Moms-id`: identifikationsnummeret, der bruges til moms- og "
"regnskabsformål. Dette kan vises som :guilabel:`Identifikationsnummer` "
"eller :guilabel:`Borger-id` afhængigt af landet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner Level`: select the designated :ref:`partner <contacts/"
"partner-assignment>` level for this contact from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Partnerniveau`: vælg det tildelte :ref:`partnerniveau <contacts/"
"partner-assignment>` for denne kontakt fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: enter the full website address, starting with `http` or "
"`https`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hjemmeside`: indtast den fulde webadresse, startende med `http` "
"eller `https`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Language`: enter the language used by the contact. All of the "
"emails and documents sent to this contact are then translated to the "
"selected language."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sprog`: indtast det sprog, som kontakten bruger. Alle e-mails og "
"dokumenter sendt til denne kontakt oversættes derefter til det valgte sprog."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: enter preconfigured tags by typing them in the field, or "
"clicking the drop-down menu, and selecting one. To create a new one, type "
"the new tag in the field, and click :guilabel:`Create` from the resulting "
"drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: indtast prækonfigurerede tags ved at skrive dem i feltet "
"eller klikke på rullemenuen og vælge et. For at oprette et nyt tag skal du "
"skrive det nye tag i feltet og klikke på :guilabel:`Opret` fra den "
"resulterende rullemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:68
msgid "Contacts & Addresses tab"
msgstr "Karta Kontakty a adresy"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:70
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the contact form are several tabs. On "
"the :guilabel:`Contacts & Addresses` tab, contacts can be added that are "
"associated with a :guilabel:`Company` and related addresses. For example, a "
"specific contact person for the company can be listed here."
msgstr ""
"V dolní části formuláře kontaktu je několik karet. Na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Kontakty a adresy` lze přidat kontakty, které jsou spojeny "
"se :guilabel:`Společností`, a související adresy. Zde může být například "
"uvedena konkrétní kontaktní osoba společnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:74
msgid ""
"Multiple addresses can be added to contacts. To do so, click :guilabel:`Add` "
"in the :guilabel:`Contacts & Addresses` tab. Doing so reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form, in which additional addresses can "
"be configured."
msgstr ""
"Der kan tilføjes flere adresser til kontakter. Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj` i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Kontakter og adresser`. Herved vises en pop op-formular med "
"titlen :guilabel:`Opret kontakt`, hvor yderligere adresser kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:78
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form, select one of the following "
"options for the address type:"
msgstr ""
"I pop op-formularen :guilabel:`Opret kontakt` skal du vælge en af følgende "
"muligheder for adressetypen:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:81
msgid ":guilabel:`Contact`: adds another contact to the existing contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kontakt`: tilføjer en anden kontakt til den eksisterende "
"kontaktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Address`: adds a specific invoice address to the existing "
"contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fakturační adresa`: přidá konkrétní fakturační adresu k "
"existujícímu formuláři kontaktu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Address`: adds a specific delivery address to the "
"existing contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodací adresa`: přidá konkrétní dodací adresu k existujícímu "
"formuláři kontaktu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Follow-up Address`: adds a preferred address for follow-up "
"reports and reminders about overdue invoices."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opfølgningsadresse`: tilføjer en foretrukken adresse til "
"opfølgningsrapporter og påmindelser om forfaldne fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other Address`: adds an alternate address for the company, such "
"as a subsidiary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anden adresse`: tilføjer en alternativ adresse til virksomheden, "
"f.eks. et datterselskab."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:None
msgid "Add a contact/address to the contact form."
msgstr "Tilføj en kontakt/adresse til kontaktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:91
msgid ""
"Once an option is selected, enter the corresponding contact information that "
"should be used for the specified address type."
msgstr ""
"Når en mulighed er valgt, indtast de tilsvarende kontaktoplysninger, der "
"skal bruges til den angivne adressetype."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:94
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`Contact Name`, :guilabel:`Address`, :guilabel:`Email`, "
"along with the :guilabel:`Phone` and :guilabel:`Mobile` numbers below."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj :guilabel:`Kontaktnavn`, :guilabel:`Adresse`, :guilabel:`E-mail` "
"samt :guilabel:`Telefon`- og :guilabel:`Mobil`numre nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:97
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Job Position`, which appears if the :guilabel:`Contact` "
"address type has been selected. This is similar to "
"the :guilabel:`Individual` contact."
msgstr ""
"Nastavte :guilabel:`Pracovní pozici`, která se zobrazí, pokud byl vybrán typ "
"adresy :guilabel:`Kontakt`. To je podobné jako u kontaktu "
"typu :guilabel:`Jednotlivec`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:100
msgid ""
"To add a note, click on the text field next to :guilabel:`Notes`, and write "
"anything that is applicable to the customer or contact."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en note skal du klikke på tekstfeltet ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Noter` og skrive alt, der er relevant for kunden eller "
"kontakten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:103
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to save the address, and close "
"the :guilabel:`Create Contact` window. Or, click :guilabel:`Save & New` to "
"save the address, and immediately input another one."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem & luk` for at gemme adressen og lukke "
"vinduet :guilabel:`Opret kontakt`. Eller klik på :guilabel:`Gem & ny` for at "
"gemme adressen og straks indtaste en ny."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:107
msgid "Sales & Purchase tab"
msgstr "Fanen Salg & indkøb"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:109
msgid ""
"Next, is the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchases` tab, which only appears when the "
"**Sales**, **Purchase**, or **Point of Sale** applications are installed."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst findes fanen :guilabel:`Salg og indkøb`, som kun vises, når "
"applikationerne **Salg**, **Indkøb** eller **POS** er installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:112
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` can be set on the :guilabel:`Sales & "
"Purchases` tab. Select a :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skatteposition` kan indstilles på fanen :guilabel:`Salg & "
"indkøb`. Vælg en :guilabel:`Skatteposition` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:118
msgid "Sales section"
msgstr "Sektionen Salg"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:120
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Sales` heading, a specific :guilabel:`Salesperson` can "
"be assigned to a contact. To do that, click the :guilabel:`Salesperson` drop-"
"down field, and select one. Create a new :guilabel:`Salesperson` by typing "
"the user's name, and making the appropriate selection."
msgstr ""
"Under overskriften :guilabel:`Salg` kan en specifik :guilabel:`Sælger` "
"tildeles en kontakt. Klik på rullefeltet :guilabel:`Sælger`, og vælg en. "
"Opret en ny :guilabel:`Sælger` ved at skrive brugerens navn og foretage det "
"relevante valg."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:124
msgid ""
"Certain :guilabel:`Payment Terms`,  a :guilabel:`Payment Method`, or a "
"specific :guilabel:`Pricelist`, can also be set, if needed. Click the drop-"
"down menu next to :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, and change it to one of the "
"preselected :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, or :guilabel:`Create` a new one. "
"Select the :guilabel:`Pricelist` drop-down menu to choose the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Pricelist`."
msgstr ""
"Visse :guilabel:`Betalingsbetingelser`, en :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode` eller "
"en specifik :guilabel:`Prisliste` kan også indstilles, hvis det er "
"nødvendigt. Klik på rullemenuen ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Betalingsbetingelser`, og skift den til en af de "
"forudvalgte :guilabel:`Betalingsbetingelser`, eller :guilabel:`Opret` en ny. "
"Vælg rullemenuen :guilabel:`Prisliste` for at vælge den "
"relevante :guilabel:`Prisliste`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click into the :guilabel:`Delivery Method` field to select an option from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Klik i feltet :guilabel:`Leveringsmetode` for at vælge en mulighed fra "
"rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:133
msgid "Point Of Sale section"
msgstr "Sektionen POS"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:135
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Point Of Sale` heading, enter a :guilabel:`Barcode` "
"that can be used to identify the contact."
msgstr ""
"Under overskriften :guilabel:`POS` skal du indtaste "
"en :guilabel:`Stregkode`, der kan bruges til at identificere kontakten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:139
msgid "Purchase section"
msgstr "Sektionen Indkøb"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:141
msgid ""
"Specify :guilabel:`Payment Terms`, :guilabel:`1099 Box` information, and a "
"preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` here. A :guilabel:`Receipt Reminder` "
"can be set here, as well."
msgstr ""
"Zde zadejte :guilabel:`Platební podmínky`, informace o :guilabel:`1099 Box` "
"a preferovanou :guilabel:`Platební metodu`. Zde lze také "
"nastavit :guilabel:`Připomínku příjmu`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:145
msgid "Misc section"
msgstr "Sektionen Diverse"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:147
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Misc.` heading, enter a :guilabel:`Citizen "
"Identification` number, if necessary for tax purposes. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Reference` field to add any additional information for this "
"contact."
msgstr ""
"Under overskriften :guilabel:`Diverse` skal du indtaste "
"et :guilabel:`Borgeridentifikationsnummer`, hvis det er nødvendigt af "
"skattemæssige årsager. Brug feltet :guilabel:`Reference` til at tilføje "
"yderligere oplysninger om denne kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:151
msgid ""
"If this contact should **only** be accessible for one company in a multi-"
"company database, select it from the :guilabel:`Company` field drop-down "
"list. Use the :guilabel:`Website` drop-down menu to restrict the publishing "
"of this contact to one website (if working on a database with multiple "
"websites). Select one or more :guilabel:`Website Tags` to assist in "
"filtering published customers on the `/customers` website page."
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne kontakt **kun** skal være tilgængelig for én virksomhed i en "
"database med flere virksomheder, skal den vælges fra rullemenuen i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Virksomhed`. Brug rullemenuen :guilabel:`Hjemmeside` til "
"at begrænse offentliggørelsen af denne kontakt til én hjemmeside (hvis du "
"arbejder på en database med flere hjemmesider). Vælg et eller "
"flere :guilabel:`Hjemmesidetags` for at hjælpe med filtrering af "
"offentliggjorte kunder på hjemmesidesiden `/customers`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:157
msgid ""
"Select an :guilabel:`Industry` for this contact from the drop-down menu. Use "
"the :guilabel:`SLA Policies` field to assign a **Helpdesk** SLA policy to "
"this contact."
msgstr ""
"Vælg en :guilabel:`Branche` for denne kontakt fra rullemenuen. Brug "
"feltet :guilabel:`SLA-politikker` til at tildele en SLA-politik fra "
"**Kundeservice** til denne kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:163
msgid "Accounting tab"
msgstr "Fanen Regnskab"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:165
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Accounting` tab appears when the **Accounting** application "
"is installed. Here, a user can add any related :guilabel:`Bank Accounts`, or "
"set default :guilabel:`Accounting entries`."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Bogføring` vises, når applikationen **Bogføring** er "
"installeret. Her kan en bruger tilføje relaterede :guilabel:`Bankkonti` "
"eller indstille standard :guilabel:`Regnskabsposteringer`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:168
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous` heading, use the :guilabel:`LEI` field "
"to enter a Legal Entity Identifier, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Pod nadpisem :guilabel:`Různé` použijte pole :guilabel:`LEI` k zadání "
"identifikátoru právnické osoby, pokud je to nutné."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:172
msgid "Internal Notes tab"
msgstr "Fanen Interne noter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:174
msgid ""
"Following the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab is the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` "
"tab, where notes can be left on this contact form, just like on the contact "
"form noted above."
msgstr ""
"Efter fanen :guilabel:`Regnskab` følger fanen :guilabel:`Interne noter`, "
"hvor der kan efterlades noter på denne kontaktformular, ligesom på "
"kontaktformularen nævnt ovenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:180
msgid "Partner Assignment tab"
msgstr "Fanen Partnertildeling"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:182
msgid ""
"Next is the :guilabel:`Partner Assignment` tab, which by default includes "
"a :guilabel:`Geolocation` section, and other partner options, "
"including :guilabel:`Partner Activation` and :guilabel:`Partner Review` "
"configurations. These are **only** present when the **Resellers** module is "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Dernæst findes fanen :guilabel:`Partnertildeling`, som som standard "
"inkluderer en sektion med :guilabel:`Geolokalisering` og andre "
"partnerindstillinger, herunder konfigurationer "
"af :guilabel:`Partneraktivering` og :guilabel:`Partnergennemgang`. Disse er "
"**kun** til stede, når modulet **Forhandlere** er installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:187
msgid ""
"Follow the :doc:`Resellers documentation <../sales/crm/track_leads/"
"resellers>` for more information on publishing partners on the website."
msgstr ""
"Følg :doc:`dokumentationen om forhandlere <../sales/crm/track_leads/"
"resellers>` for mere information om at publicere partnere på hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:191
msgid "Membership tab"
msgstr "Karta Členství"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:193
msgid ""
"Finally, there is the :guilabel:`Membership` tab on contact forms, which can "
"help users manage any memberships that are being offered to this specific "
"contact. It should be noted that this tab **only** appears when the "
"*Members* application is installed."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec je na formulářích kontaktů karta :guilabel:`Členství`, která může "
"uživatelům pomoci spravovat veškerá členství nabízená tomuto konkrétnímu "
"kontaktu. Je třeba poznamenat, že tato karta se zobrazuje **pouze** v "
"případě, že je nainstalována aplikace *Members*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:198
msgid "Activate membership"
msgstr "Aktivovat členství"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:200
msgid ""
"To activate a contact's membership, click :guilabel:`Buy Membership` in "
"the :guilabel:`Membership` tab of a contact form. On the pop-up window that "
"appears, select a :guilabel:`Membership` from the drop-down menu. Then, "
"configure a :guilabel:`Member Price`. Click :guilabel:`Invoice Membership` "
"when both fields are filled in."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li aktivovat členství kontaktu, klikněte na :guilabel:`Koupit "
"členství` na kartě :guilabel:`Členství` formuláře kontaktu. Ve vyskakovacím "
"okně, které se zobrazí, vyberte :guilabel:`Členství` z rozevírací nabídky. "
"Poté nakonfigurujte :guilabel:`Cenu pro člena`. Po vyplnění obou polí "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Fakturovat členství`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:205
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to offer a free membership, tick the :guilabel:`Free Member` "
"checkbox, in the :guilabel:`Membership` tab of a contact form."
msgstr ""
"Případně můžete nabídnout bezplatné členství zaškrtnutím "
"políčka :guilabel:`Bezplatný člen` na kartě :guilabel:`Členství` formuláře "
"kontaktu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:209
msgid ""
"Follow the :doc:`Members documentation <../sales/members>` for more "
"information on publishing members on the website."
msgstr ""
"Pro více informací o zveřejňování členů na webových stránkách postupujte "
"podle :doc:`dokumentace Members <../sales/members>`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:213
msgid "Smart buttons"
msgstr "Intelligente knapper"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:215
msgid ""
"At the top of the contact form, there are some additional options available, "
"known as *smart buttons*."
msgstr ""
"Øverst i kontaktformularen er der nogle yderligere tilgængelige muligheder, "
"kendt som *smarte knapper*."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:218
msgid ""
"Here, Odoo displays a variety of records, related to this contact, that were "
"created on other apps. Odoo integrates information from every single app, so "
"there are many smart buttons."
msgstr ""
"Her viser Odoo en række poster relateret til denne kontakt, som blev "
"oprettet i andre apps. Odoo integrerer information fra hver eneste app, så "
"der er mange smarte knapper."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:222
msgid ""
"For example, there is an :guilabel:`Opportunities` smart button, where all "
"the opportunities related to this customer from the **CRM** app are "
"accessible."
msgstr ""
"Der er for eksempel en smart-knap med titlen :guilabel:`Muligheder`, hvor "
"alle de muligheder, der er relateret til denne kunde fra appen **CRM**, er "
"tilgængelige."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:226
msgid ""
"If the corresponding applications are installed, their related smart buttons "
"appear automatically on a contact form."
msgstr ""
"Hvis de tilsvarende applikationer er installeret, vises deres relaterede "
"smarte knapper automatisk på en kontaktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:229
msgid ""
"A user can see any :guilabel:`Meetings`, :guilabel:`Sales`, :guilabel:`POS "
"Orders`, :guilabel:`Subscriptions`, project :guilabel:`Tasks`, and "
"the :guilabel:`More` smart button reveals additional options, via a drop-"
"down menu. A user can even quickly "
"access :guilabel:`Purchases`, :guilabel:`Helpdesk` tasks, :guilabel:`On-time "
"Rate` for deliveries, :guilabel:`Invoiced` information, :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Bills`, and the :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` connected to this contact."
msgstr ""
"En bruger kan se "
"eventuelle :guilabel:`Møder`, :guilabel:`Salg`, :guilabel:`POS-"
"ordrer`, :guilabel:`Abonnementer`, projekt-:guilabel:`Opgaver`, og den "
"smarte knap :guilabel:`Mere` afslører yderligere muligheder via en "
"rullemenu. En bruger kan endda hurtigt "
"tilgå :guilabel:`Indkøb`, :guilabel:`Kundeservice`-"
"opgaver, :guilabel:`Rettidighed` for leveringer, :guilabel:`Faktureret`-"
"information, :guilabel:`Kreditorfakturaer` og :guilabel:`Partnerreskontroen` "
"tilknyttet denne kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:235
msgid ""
"Deliveries, documents, loyalty cards, and direct debits are also linked to "
"smart buttons, like this, should there be any related to this contact."
msgstr ""
"Leveringer, dokumenter, loyalitetskort og direkte debiteringer er også "
"knyttet til smart-knapper som denne, hvis der er nogen relateret til denne "
"kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:238
msgid ""
"If the contact is a partner, the user can visit their partner page on the "
"Odoo-built website by clicking the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kontakten er en partner, kan brugeren besøge deres partnerside på den "
"Odoo-byggede hjemmeside ved at klikke på den smarte knap :guilabel:`Gå til "
"hjemmeside`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:242
msgid "Archive contacts"
msgstr "Arkiver kontakter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:244
msgid ""
"If a user decides they no longer want to have this contact active, the "
"record can be archived. To do that, go to the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu at the top of the contact form, and "
"click :guilabel:`Archive`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en bruger beslutter, at de ikke længere ønsker at have denne kontakt "
"aktiv, kan posten arkiveres. For at gøre det, gå til menuen :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Handling` øverst i kontaktformularen, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Arkiver`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:248
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Archive` from the resulting :guilabel:`Confirmation` "
"pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`arkiver` fra det viste pop op-"
"vindue :guilabel:`bekræftelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:250
msgid ""
"With this contact successfully archived, as indicated by a banner at the "
"top, they do not show up in the main contacts page, but they can still be "
"searched for with the :guilabel:`Archived` filter."
msgstr ""
"Når denne kontakt er succesfuldt arkiveret, som angivet af et banner øverst, "
"vises de ikke på hovedsiden for kontakter, men de kan stadig søges efter med "
"filteret :guilabel:`Arkiveret`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:254
msgid ""
"A contact can be *unarchived*, if the user decides to work with them again. "
"To do that, just click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu again at "
"the top of the archived contact form, and click :guilabel:`Unarchive`. Upon "
"doing so, the :guilabel:`Archived` banner is removed, and the contact is "
"restored."
msgstr ""
"En kontakt kan *genaktiveres*, hvis brugeren beslutter at arbejde med dem "
"igen. For at gøre det skal du blot klikke på menuen :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Handling` igen øverst i den arkiverede kontaktformular og "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Genaktiver`. Ved at gøre det fjernes "
"banneret :guilabel:`Arkiveret`, og kontakten gendannes."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:260
msgid ""
":doc:`Add different addresses in CRM <../sales/sales/sales_quotations/"
"different_addresses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Tilføj forskellige adresser i CRM <../sales/sales/sales_quotations/"
"different_addresses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts.rst:261
msgid ""
"`Odoo's eLearning Contacts tutorial <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"contacts-2527?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoos eLearning-tutorial om kontakter <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"contacts-2527?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:3
msgid "Merge contacts"
msgstr "Flet kontakter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's *Contacts* application allows user's to merge duplicate contacts, "
"without losing any information in the process. This keeps the database "
"organized, and prevents contacts from being contacted by more than one "
"salesperson."
msgstr ""
"Odoos *Adressebog*-applikation giver brugere mulighed for at flette "
"duplikerede kontakter uden at miste nogen information i processen. Dette "
"holder databasen organiseret og forhindrer, at kontakter kontaktes af mere "
"end én sælger."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:12
msgid "Merge duplicate contacts"
msgstr "Flet duplikerede kontakter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:15
msgid ""
"Merging is an irreversible action. Do **not** merge contacts unless "
"absolutely certain they should be combined."
msgstr ""
"Fletning er en irreversibel handling. Flet **ikke** kontakter, medmindre du "
"er helt sikker på, at de skal kombineres."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:18
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Contacts app`, and select the :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(list)` icon. Select two or more duplicate contacts from "
"the list, and tick the checkbox (on the far-left) for the contacts that "
"should be merged. Then, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon, "
"and select :guilabel:`Merge` from the resulting drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Adressebog-appen`, og vælg ikonet :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(liste)`. Vælg to eller flere duplikerede kontakter fra "
"listen, og marker afkrydsningsfeltet (helt til venstre) for de kontakter, "
"der skal flettes. Klik derefter på ikonet :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Handlinger`, og vælg :guilabel:`Flet` fra den resulterende "
"rullemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:None
msgid "The merge contacts option in the Contacts application."
msgstr "Muligheden for at sammenflette kontakter i Adressebog-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:27
msgid ""
"This opens the :guilabel:`Merge` pop-up window. From here, review the "
"details of the contacts before confirming they should be merged. If any "
"contacts in the list should **not** be merged, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(delete)` icon at the far right of the contact."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Sammenflet`. Herfra kan du gennemse "
"kontaktoplysningerne, før du bekræfter, at de skal sammenflettes. Hvis nogen "
"kontakter på listen **ikke** skal sammenflettes, skal du klikke på "
"ikonet :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(slet)` længst til højre for kontakten."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:32
msgid ""
"Click the individual contact to open the record for that contact, and view "
"additional information."
msgstr ""
"Klik på den enkelte kontakt for at åbne posten for den pågældende kontakt og "
"se yderligere oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:None
msgid "The merge pop-up window in the Contacts application."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet til sammenfletning i Adressebog-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:39
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Destination Contact` field, and select an option from "
"the drop-down list. This field defaults to the contact record that was "
"created first in the system."
msgstr ""
"Klik på feltet :guilabel:`Destinationskontakt`, og vælg en mulighed fra "
"rullelisten. Dette felt er som standard indstillet til den kontaktpost, der "
"blev oprettet først i systemet."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:42
msgid ""
"After confirming the information on the pop-up window, "
"click :guilabel:`Merge Contacts`."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have bekræftet oplysningerne i pop op-vinduet skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Sammenflet kontakter`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:45
msgid "Deduplicate contacts"
msgstr "Fjerne dubletter af kontakter"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:47
msgid ""
"After the merge is finished, a pop-up window appears confirming it is "
"complete. This pop-up window also contains a :guilabel:`Deduplicate the "
"other Contacts` button. This feature searches for duplicated records, based "
"on selected criteria, and merges them automatically, or after manual "
"approval."
msgstr ""
"Når sammenfletningen er færdig, vises et pop op-vindue, der bekræfter, at "
"den er fuldført. Dette pop op-vindue indeholder også en "
"knap :guilabel:`Fjern dubletter af de andre kontakter`. Denne funktion søger "
"efter duplikerede poster baseret på udvalgte kriterier og sammenfletter dem "
"automatisk eller efter manuel godkendelse."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:52
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Deduplicate the other Contacts` button to open "
"the :guilabel:`Deduplicate Contacts` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Fjern dubletter af de andre kontakter` for at "
"åbne pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Fjern dubletter af kontakter`."

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:55
msgid ""
"Select one or more fields to be used in the search for duplicated records. "
"Duplicated contacts can be searched, based on the following criteria:"
msgstr ""
"Vælg et eller flere felter, der skal bruges i søgningen efter duplikerede "
"poster. Duplikerede kontakter kan søges baseret på følgende kriterier:"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:58
msgid ":guilabel:`Email`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`E-mail`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:59
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Navn`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:60
msgid ":guilabel:`Is Company`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Er en virksomhed`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`CVR`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/contacts/merge.rst:62
msgid ":guilabel:`Parent Company`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Moderselskab`"

